            <title>[SHIRO-234] ClassCastException in checkRoles</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SHIRO-234</link>
                <project id="12310950" key="SHIRO">Shiro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I get the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java.lang.ClassCastException: [Ljava.lang.Object; cannot be cast to [Ljava.lang.String;&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.shiro.authz.ModularRealmAuthorizer.checkRoles(ModularRealmAuthorizer.java:426)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In checkRoles, the collection is incorrectly cast to a String[]. The line needs to do toArray(new String&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;roles.size&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;) and not toArray().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
